<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Effects of fire patterns are unknown but likely detrimental. <i>Menodora spinescens </i>is apparently frost sensitive, despite its occupation of mid-elevation sites. Webb et al. (2003) reported severe reduction of <i>M. spinescens </i>cover after the hard freeze in 1990.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
